msgid ""
"Odds ratio indicates the following: <br> (Ratio > 1): Group <em>%1$s</em> is "
"more likely in group <em>%2$s</em><br>(Ratio < 1): Group <em>%1$s</em> is "
"less likely in group <em>%2$s</em>"
