"Log odds ratio indicates the following:<br>(Ratio > 0): Group <em>%1$s</em> "
"is more likely in group <em>%2$s</em> <br>(Ratio < 0): Group <em>%1$s</em> "
"is less likely in group <em>%2$s</em>"
